Dear Eng. Mirzaee,


Thanks for your email. Please find the below reply.


1. New products:
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; We are surprised to hear that the new products is  canceled suddenly, which will cause two bad results:
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1) It will be difficult or impossible to execute the replacing of the data acquisition box, if only the original small box is delivered first to Iran.&nbsp; 

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Because the job of replaing box, installing new modules, wiring, and testing can only be made by the production department and before two boxes are delivered. The job needs special workers, and special tools. 

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2) It become impossible to help you reduce the 5.000 USD. We originally want to sacrifice all our profit of new product to reduce your some loss from chasing case,now if cancling new products, we can't find other way to deal with the 5,000 USD.


2. Dynamometer: 

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1) The date of shipment, currently the carriers EMK, UCL and VOLTA can deliver cargo to Abbas, the date is each Saturday (July 18, July 25, August 1).&nbsp; We need about 7 working days after receiving your payment to do the job of packing and fumigation cases. So please allow us to know your payment date.&nbsp; For example, if you pay before July 15, the shipment date July 25 is no problem. 

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2) Both the PDF version and the print copy will be sent when delivering the dynamometer.


3. Payments:
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Your requirement can't be accepted by CAMA. 

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The central theme as mentioned before, is: CAMA is a state-owned company, the 2019 signed dynamometer contract was hand on and record in AVIC group, and the amount 280,000 USD can't be reduced at random. 

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; What we can do is helping you to reduce some lost from future contracts, through lowest product price. 

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1) CAMA can't take the 35.000 USD. 

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Nobody can prevent their mailbox from being hacked by premeditated criminal, what they can do is                          enhancing their vigilance and not believing the cheater's words. We even reminded you via Wechat and email before you transferred on August 14, 2019. It's not&nbsp; CAMA's fault. The hateful cheater should be seized and you should get back of lost from them. 

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2) 5.000 USD can't be reduced from the dynamomer contract.
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The reason has been told above.&nbsp; 

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The cancel of experts trip is due to force majeure. If can't be reduced through new products contract, CAMA guarantee the experts' trip is effective in the following 10 years, welcome to CAMA, Luoyang at any your convenience time. 

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Frankly speaking, the experts trip was strongly required to add by Mr. Damghani in Iran embassy, before that all our quotation never included. Because of this contract profit is too low, the trip budget has to be calculated into other guest accommodation activity, the company can only reimburse according to the actual  expenses. No actual trip and expense, how can we get the money? 

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
Dear Eng. Mirzaee, till now we also feel very tired and failed about this contract, tiny profit, large advance funds, so long period, if calculating the inventory loss and capital turnover, CAMA has already lost money from this contract, not earn money.&nbsp; For more requirement of reducing amount, how can we bear? 





Hope you can understand. 


&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 

Best wishes


Holly Li
