Hello

We would like to thank you for your effort regarding to chasing the lost money from police.

The new products:  
The user has decided to purchase the goods soon in the future; therefore the procedure of purchasing the new products is canceled in this phase.


Dynamometer;  
As the user accepted the videos regarding the tests we are ready to receive the goods.

Based upon point 5.2 of the contract the seller is supposed to provide a formal letter in which the date of shipment is mentioned. You are kindly asked to send the letter.

You were asked to send us the manual of the products which we have been told need to be translated, in case the translation is over please let us have the manual.


Payments;  
Due to the loss has happened we have the decision to chase track the case officially; therefore we believe as both sides’ emails were hacked you should accept half of the lost money, equals 35.000 USD. In case 70.000 USD is taken back from the hacker, your money will be transmitted to you again.

Previously you have reduced 5.000 USD from the price of the new products as the trip of our experts has been cancelled to China. As the purchase of the new products has been cancelled, we should have the reduction for the contract.


We hope the mentioned issued are accepted by you so we can continue the procedure.

